quran[9{c,v,t}:
34,40,aur jis din woh un sab ko jama kere ga phir firshton se farmaiye gakiya yeh log tum ko pooja karte they
34,41,woh kahin ge to pak hai to hi hamara dost hai. nah yeh. balkay yeh jaanat ko pooja karte they. aur aksar unhi ko mantay they
34,42,to aaj tum mein se koi kisi ko naffa aur nuqsaan pohanchanay ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhta. aur hum zaalmon se kahin ge ke dozakh ke azaab ka jis ko tum jhoot samajte they maza chako
34,43,aur jab un ko hamari roshan ayatain parh kar sunai jati hain to kehte hain yeh aik ( aisa ) shakhs hai jo chahta hai ke jin cheezon ki tumahray baap dada parastishkiya karte they un se tum ko rok day aur ( yeh bhi ) kehte hain ke yeh ( quran ) mehez jhoot hai ( jo apni taraf se ) bana liya gaya hai. aur kafiroon ke paas jab haq aaya to is ke baray mein kehnay lagey ke yeh to Sarih jaadoo hai
34,44,aur hum ne nah to un ( mushrikon ) ko kitaaben den jin ko yeh parhte hain aur nah tum se pehlay un ki taraf koi darane wala bheja magar unhon ne takzieeb ki
34,45,aur jo log un se pehlay they unhon ne takzieeb ki thi aur jo kuch hum ne un ko diya tha yeh is ke dasvin hissay ko bhi nahi puhanche to unhon ne mere payghambaroon ko jhtlaya. so mera azaab kaisa howa
34,46,keh do ke mein tumhe sirf aik baat ki nasiyaat karta hon ke tum khuda ke liye do do aur akailey akailey kharray hojao phir ghhor karo. tumahray Rafeeq ko soda nahi woh tum ko azaab sakht ( ke anay ) se pehlay sirf darane walay hain
34,47,keh do ke mein ne tum se kuch sila manga ho to woh tum hi ko ( mubarak rahay ). mera sila khuda hi ke zimmay hai. aur woh har cheez se khabardaar hai
34,48,keh do ke mera perwar-digaar oopar se haq utaarta hai ( aur woh ) ghaib ki baton ka jan-nay wala hai
